1) Copy 'Richard Adams.properties' and use it as a template for your own file of machine specific settings.
2) Rename the file 'user.name'.properties where user.name is  the value of the Java system property user.name.
2) Run build.xml.

For tests to run, you may need to add the junit4.4 jar from your eclipse plugin into
the ant classpath (via the classpath tab of the launch configuration).